ğŸŒ Federal University of Education, Olosoho â€“ Responsive Website

This is a sample **responsive website** built using **HTML5** and **CSS3**, showcasing a fictional university:  

**Federal University of Education, Olosoho**.

It uses **CSS Grid** and responsive design techniques to adapt smoothly across different screen sizes.

